<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA75">
<l>puviyu miruvicumpu niṉakatta nīyeṉ</l>
<l>ceviyiṉ vaḻipukunteṉ ṉuḷḷā yaviviṉṟi</l>
<l>yāṉperiya ṉīperiyai yeṉpataṉai yāraṟivā</l>
<l>rūṉparuku nēmiyā yuḷḷu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The earth and the vast sky are inside you. You, having entered</l>
<l>by the way of my ear, are not inside me. Except in annihilation,</l>
<l>who will know [how] to say I am great, you are great?</l>
<l>You with the flesh-drinking discus, reflect.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
